## What's Changed
* chore: Add a scheduled workflow to run CI every day. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/292
* chore: Enable ccache in flatpak builds. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/294
* perf: Improve performance of video frame buffering. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/276
* test: Update loginscreen UI test golden image. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/302
* fix: Avoid hanging when capture device permissions denied on macOS. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/300
* fix: Don't crash on logout. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/305
* cleanup: Fix compilation for Android 7. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/309
* fix: Don't crash when closing the app after logout. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/308
* cleanup: Add dep name in the log message file path on macOS. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/311
* cleanup: Don't connect to NULL window handle's signals. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/315
* cleanup: Normalise audio to -1.0 dB. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/316
* fix: Fix uninitialised read in contact circle widget. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/314
* cleanup: Add openal logging and audio log category. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/317
* cleanup: Add ffmpeg logging. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/318
* chore: Install Apple dev certificate for signing macOS distributables. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/319
* chore: Install homebrew bash v5. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/321
* cleanup: Don't use deprecated spelling of tox enums. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/323
* docs: Translations update from Hosted Weblate by @weblate in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/303
* chore: Update versions for the 1.18.0-rc.3 release. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/324
* chore: Only run the PR validator on pull requests. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/327
* style: Reformat CHANGELOG.md with markdown formatter. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/326
* chore: Add scripts for uploading and verifying release assets. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/329
* chore: Rewrite clog (more correctly) in Python. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/328
* chore: Add script for syncing CHANGELOG.md to git tags. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/325
* refactor: Move common python code into a library; add RCs to changelog. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/330
* feat: add appimage back to ci by @Green-Sky in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/306
* chore: Add script to automate most of the release process. by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/332
* chore: Fix appimage release build (`-` instead of `.`). by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/333
* chore: Release v1.18.0-rc.4 by @iphydf in https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/pull/331


**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/TokTok/qTox/compare/v1.18.0-rc.3...v1.18.0-rc.4
